        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-cbh-dark leading-tight">
          Life in Beaconwood: Eagle, Idaho's Most Sought-After New Community
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-cbh-slate">
          Welcome to Beaconwood, where luxury meets the laid-back spirit of Eagle, Idaho. Located in one of the Treasure Valley's most desirable neighborhoods, Beaconwood offers move-in ready homes with scenic Bogus Basin views and the peace of mind that comes from buying Idaho's most trusted builder. Every detail has been considered, from the Level 5 &amp; 6 designer interiors to the tree-lined walking paths just outside your front door.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-cbh-slate">
          Eagle, Idaho is more than a location. It's a lifestyle. Minutes from downtown Eagle with its local restaurants, boutiques, and coffee shops, Beaconwood puts you at the center of everything the Treasure Valley has to offer. Top-rated West Ada School District schools, year-round outdoor recreation from the Boise River Greenbelt to Bogus Basin ski resort, and a tight-knit community feel make Eagle the place families choose to put down roots.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-cbh-slate">
          As Idaho's #1 homebuilder for over 34 years, CBH Homes has helped more than 29,000 families find their perfect home. At Beaconwood, that legacy shows in every quartz countertop, every designer tile backsplash, and every well-designed floor plan. Tour on your schedule with a no-pressure self-guided tour, or stop by during On the Block Saturdays. Your new home is waiting.
        </p>
